Recipes Collection:
{
   "_id": ObjectId("recipe_id"),
   "name": "Recipe Name",
   "categories": ["category_id_1", "category_id_2"],
   "ingredients": [
      {
         "ingredient_id": "ingredient_id_1",
         "quantity": "100 grs"
      },
      {
         "ingredient_id": "ingredient_id_2",
         "quantity": "1 cup"
      }
   ],
   "steps": [
      {
         "step_id": "step_id_1",
         "step_order": 1,
         "description": "Step 1 Description"
      },
      {
         "step_id": "step_id_2",
         "step_order": 2,
         "description": "Step 2 Description"
      }
   ]
}

Categories Collection:
{
   "_id": ObjectId("category_id_here"),
   "name": "Category Name"
}

Steps Collection:
{
   "_id": ObjectId("step_id_here"),
   "description": "Step Description"
}

1-RecipeCategories Collection: the relationship between recipes and categories. 
2-RecipeIngredients Collection: the relationship between recipes and ingredients
3-RecipeSteps Collection: the relationship between recipes and steps,

